For details, please see wiki page:
    http://code.google.com/p/plda/wiki/PLDAQuickStart
    http://code.google.com/p/plda/wiki/PLDAManual

Compilation from root directory:
mkdir build
cd build
cmake ..
make -j4

Parallel Version:
  * built if MPI_CXX found
  * if you explicitely want to set a specific mpich2 directory do:
  * cmake -DMPI_CXX_COMPILER=PREFIX/bin/mpicxx ..
  * where PREFIX is the prefix path of your mpi installation directory
